Modifications from upstream:
- Removed non-Claude Code agent integrations (Cursor, Copilot, Codex, Windsurf)
- Removed NoirsBoxes commercial branding and sub-agent
- Removed associated MCP server and plugin configuration
- Simplified README for personal/internal use with Claude Code

The following upstream components are preserved substantially unchanged:
- Pipeline architecture and YAML manifests (pipeline_defs/)
- Stage director skill system (skills/)
- Tool registry and BaseTool contract (tools/)
- Remotion and HyperFrames composition engines
- Core infrastructure (lib/, schemas/, styles/)
- Layer 3 provider knowledge packs (.agents/skills/)
